snippet.textDisplay: Make a whole day Pass It On: A normal goes shopping. Another normal designs recipes based on the available groceries and measures the ingredients for cooking. A chef can choose to make a dessert or the main course based on cooking time. Another chef makes what the first chef didn't choose. A normal finishes by plating both the main course and the desserts. Target: Hefty meal for five with indulgent dessert. Five hours total, so every minute they save helps the next one. They can decide how long they take, but no one may do each others' tasks. No messages or recipes are passed on. Dessert may be left in the fridge/freezer and/or the main course in the oven/hob until it is time for the plating.
snippet.textOriginal: Make a whole day Pass It On: A normal goes shopping. Another normal designs recipes based on the available groceries and measures the ingredients for cooking. A chef can choose to make a dessert or the main course based on cooking time. Another chef makes what the first chef didn't choose. A normal finishes by plating both the main course and the desserts. Target: Hefty meal for five with indulgent dessert. Five hours total, so every minute they save helps the next one. They can decide how long they take, but no one may do each others' tasks. No messages or recipes are passed on. Dessert may be left in the fridge/freezer and/or the main course in the oven/hob until it is time for the plating.
